My god, I've downloaded several torrents so far today and all I'm seeing is people wanting to rate everything on the same damn scale regardless of what quality it is.

Fuck rating it on "over all quality".  Rating it based on how good it is compared to other similar formats is far better.  Of course a cam will be shit quality, but rating it based on how good it is *as* a cam tells people which cam is better and thus worth downloading.  Rating all cams a 1 because they are shit compared to bluray provides no information at all about how the cam compares to other cams.

BTW, the dvd/bluray release date is June 26th in the US.

If you live in a different country where it's already out, then don't bitch because the uploader isn't living in your country.
